edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification
Class BlockType

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification.BlockType

public class BlockType
extends java.lang.Object

The BlockType class represents one of the block types for a specific FPGA family (i.e. V4, V5, V6). Each family should have a Set of BlockTypes that indicates the valid block types that are used by the family. Each BlockType has a List of SubBlockTypes indicating the valid column types for the block.
